channel.name: Export 1: Export From Excel
channel.description:
This channel will serve up an Excel spread sheet which has a button that can be used to export the data of any Excel table in this sheet back into this Iguana web service.
See http://help.interfaceware.com/v6/excel-exporter
Use this channel with the From Excel Exporter.
